high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the wall, then turn right again and walk up to the end of the island.
Pick up the sweet potato off of the kitchen island.
Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Put the sweet potato in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and take out the now clean sweet potato.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the oven and look up at the microwave.
Put the clean sweet potato in the microwave and then close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sweet potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and step forward, then turn left to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the potato from the kitchen island.
Turn left and go toward the fridge, then turn right and move forward, then turn left to go to the sink.
Wash the potato in the sink.
Turn around, then turn left and go toward the stove, then look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the potato inside.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around toward the green table.
Pick up the potato next to the spatula.
Turn left and head across the room to the sink.
Rinse the potato in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn left and go to the stove.
Put the potato in the microwave on the right side of the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato in the microwave.
